<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Don't Miss Out - Engagematic</title>
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f5f5f5;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
        }

        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            padding: 40px 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .header h1 {
            color: #ffffff;
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 28px;
        }

        .content {
            padding: 40px 30px;
        }

        .content h2 {
            color: #333333;
            font-size: 24px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .content p {
            color: #666666;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            font-size: 16px;
        }

        .value-box {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #00b894 0%, #00cec9 100%);
            color: #ffffff;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            margin: 25px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .value-box h3 {
            margin: 0 0 15px 0;
            font-size: 22px;
        }

        .feature-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 15px;
            margin: 25px 0;
        }

        .feature-item {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .feature-item h4 {
            color: #667eea;
            margin: 0 0 10px 0;
            font-size: 16px;
        }

        .cta-button {
            display: inline-block;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            color: #ffffff;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 15px 40px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin: 20px 0;
            font-size: 16px;
        }

        .footer {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
            color: #999999;
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        .footer a {
            color: #667eea;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>You're Missing Out!</h1>
        </div>

        <div class="content">
            <h2>Hi <%= name || 'there' %>,</h2>

            <p>We noticed you haven't been active on Engagematic recently. We wanted to remind you of the value you're missing!</p>

            <div class="value-box">
                <h3>Your Progress So Far</h3>
                <p style="font-size: 18px; margin: 15px 0;">
                    You've created <strong><%= postsCount || '0' %> posts</strong> and generated <strong><%= engagementCount || '0' %> engagements</strong>!
                </p>
                <p style="opacity: 0.9;">Keep the momentum going!</p>
            </div>

            <p><strong>What You Can Still Do:</strong></p>
            <div class="feature-grid">
                <div class="feature-item">
                    <h4>Create Posts</h4>
                    <p style="color: #666666; font-size: 14px; margin: 0;"><%= postsRemaining || '0' %> posts remaining</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-item">
                    <h4>Generate Comments</h4>
                    <p style="color: #666666; font-size: 14px; margin: 0;"><%= commentsRemaining || '0' %> comments remaining</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-item">
                    <h4>View Analytics</h4>
                    <p style="color: #666666; font-size: 14px; margin: 0;">Track your performance</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-item">
                    <h4>Use Templates</h4>
                    <p style="color: #666666; font-size: 14px; margin: 0;">Access all templates</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <p><strong>Don't let your subscription go to waste!</strong></p>
            <ul style="color: #666666; line-height: 1.8;">
                <li>You're already paying for these features</li>
                <li>Your usage limits reset soon</li>
                <li>Create content now to maximize value</li>
                <li>Build your LinkedIn presence consistently</li>
            </ul>

            <div style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
                <a href="<%= dashboardUrl %>" class="cta-button">
                    Start Creating Now â†’
                </a>
            </div>

            <p style="margin-top: 30px;">Need help getting started? Reply to this email and we'll provide personalized tips to help you make the most of Engagematic!</p>

            <p style="margin-top: 30px;">Best regards,<br><strong>The Engagematic Team</strong></p>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>&copy; <%= currentYear %> Engagematic. All rights reserved.</p>
            <p>
                <a href="<%= preferencesUrl %>">Email Preferences</a> |
                <a href="<%= unsubscribeUrl %>">Unsubscribe</a>
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>

